           fhir:v "/*\n@dynamicValue: Bacille Calmette–Guérin (BCG) dose 1 Due Date\n@pseudocode: \"Date of birth\"\n*/\ndefine \"Bacille Calmette–Guérin (BCG) dose 1 Due Date\":\n  Patient.birthDate"
